Paris Saint-Germain have opened discussions with Paul Pogba over a possible move from Juventus .
The Italian champions were kept informed no formal offer has yet been made to the club .
Pogba and his representatives are understood to have met PSG president Nasser Al Khelaifi in Monte Carlo on Tuesday .
Sevilla are weighing up a move for Manchester City 's 29-year-old winger Jesus Navas in the Champions League .